      <reaction metaid="metaid_761" id="reaction_377644" name="Release of CSK from SRC" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">CSK bound to integrin alphaIIb beta3 negatively regulates SRC by phosphorylating the Tyr-530. Platelet adhesion to fibrinogen causes the disassociation of CSK from alphaIIb beta3 complex.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
