      <reaction metaid="metaid_813" id="reaction_199093" name="CXADR binds to AMICA1" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_876">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">JAM members, such as JAML, bind coxsackie and adenovirus receptor (CXADR) on epithelial and endothelial cells.</p>
