      <reaction metaid="metaid_823" id="reaction_481010" name="Surface deployment of platelet dense granule membrane components" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_876">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Constituents of the platelet dense granule membrane are incorporated into the platelet membrane following exocytosis of granule content.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
