      <reaction metaid="metaid_827" id="reaction_114671" name="vWF binds to collagen" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_984">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">At the beginning of this reaction, 1 molecule of &apos;Collagen I&apos;, and 1 molecule of &apos;Von Willebrand factor precursor&apos; are present. At the end of this reaction, 1 molecule of &apos;Collagen IV : vWF complex&apos; is present.</p>
        </notes>
