      <reaction metaid="metaid_838" id="reaction_210977" name="Sos-mediated nucleotide exchange of Ras (Tie2 receptor:Grb2:Sos)" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Sos-1 bound to Grb2:Tie2 complex promotes the exchange of inactive Ras-GDP to active Ras-GTP (Boriack-Sjodin et al.1998, Khan et al. 2004).</p>
