      <reaction metaid="metaid_856" id="reaction_418170" name="F2R:ARRB1 binds MAPKs, SRC-1" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Beta-arrestins can serve as scaffolding molecules that facilitate G-protein independent cell signaling</p>
        </notes>
