      <reaction metaid="metaid_878" id="reaction_114684" name="Phosphorylation of Syntaxin-4" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">At the beginning of this reaction, 1 molecule of &apos;ATP&apos;, and 1 molecule of &apos;Syntaxin 4&apos; are present. At the end of this reaction, 1 molecule of &apos;Phosphorylated syntaxin 4&apos;, and 1 molecule of &apos;ADP&apos; are present. This reaction is mediated by the &apos;calcium-dependent protein kinase C activity&apos; of &apos;Activated Ca++ and DAG dependent PKC&apos;.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
