      <reaction metaid="metaid_887" id="reaction_425861" name="Activation of Protein Kinase C novel isoforms" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Activation of the novel Protein Kinase C (nPKC) isoforms (delta, epsilon, eta and theta) requires binding to the membrane lipid diacylglycerol (DAG). nPKC activation is sensitive to DAG concentration.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
          <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:vCard="http://www.w3.org/2001/vcard-rdf/3.0#" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:bqbiol="http://biomodels.net/biology-qualifiers/">
