      <reaction metaid="metaid_907" id="reaction_1008248" name="Adenylate Kinase 3 is a GTP-AMP phosphotransferase" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_5460">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">GTP-AMP phosphotransferase, also called Adenylate kinase 3 catalyzes phosphate transfer from GTP to AMP (EC 2.7.4.10). A crystal structure is available (Choe et al. 2005).</p>
        </notes>
