      <reaction metaid="metaid_917" id="reaction_140870" name="thrombin:antithrombin III:heparan sulfate -&gt; thrombin:cleaved antithrombin III:heparan sulfate" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_876">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Antithrombin III in the complex is cleaved by thrombin, thereupon undergoing a conformational change that stabilizes the thrombin:antithrombin III complex, trapping and inactivating the thrombin moiety.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
          <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:vCard="http://www.w3.org/2001/vcard-rdf/3.0#" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:bqbiol="http://biomodels.net/biology-qualifiers/">
