      <reaction metaid="metaid_938" id="reaction_8948034" name="FGR binds LDL:LRP8" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_876">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Tyrosine phosphorylation of LDL:LRP8 is mediated by the Src-family kinase FGR, based on a correlation of increased LRP8 phosphorylation in LDL-stimulated platelets and a transient increased co-precipitation of FGR and LRP8 upon LDL stimulation.</p>
        </notes>
