      <reaction metaid="metaid_953" id="reaction_204773" name="Interaction of Tie2 and Grb7" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_876">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Grb7 was initially identified as an EGF receptor binding protein and thereafter many binding partners have been reported. Grb7 interacts with Tie2/Tek in a phosphotyrosine-dependent manner through its SH2 domain.</p>
        </notes>
