      <reaction metaid="metaid_961" id="reaction_482772" name="Release of platelet cytosolic components" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Platelet releasate contains a range of proteins that do not originate in specialized storage granules. In some cases platelet lysis may contribute to the presence of these proteins in the platelet relesate.</p>
