      <reaction metaid="metaid_962" id="reaction_437192" name="PDPK1 binds PRKCZ" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">3-phosphoinositide dependent protein kinase-1 (PDPK1, also known as PDK1) and Protein kinase C zeta type (PRKCZ, also known as PKC zeta) are associated in fibroblasts.</p>
