      <reaction metaid="metaid_971" id="reaction_354165" name="Interaction of SOS with GRB2 bound to FADK1" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Son of sevenless protein homolog 1(SOS) is an activating nucleotide exchange factor for H-Ras (p21Ras). SOS is brought close to the H-Ras by interacting with the FADK1 bound GRB2.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
          <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:vCard="http://www.w3.org/2001/vcard-rdf/3.0#" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:bqbiol="http://biomodels.net/biology-qualifiers/">
