      <reaction metaid="metaid_982" id="reaction_140872" name="thrombin:cleaved SERPINC1:HSPGs-&gt; thrombin:cleaved SERPINC1 + HSPGs" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_984">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The same conformational change that traps thrombin in its complex with cleaved antithrombin III also decreases the affinity of the latter for heparin, and the complex of cleaved antithrombin III and thrombin dissociates from the cell-bound heparin molecule.</p>
        </notes>
