      <reaction metaid="metaid_989" id="reaction_114683" name="Phosphorylation of Platelet Sec-1" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">At the beginning of this reaction, 1 molecule of &apos;ATP&apos;, and 1 molecule of &apos;Platelet SEC1 protein&apos; are present. At the end of this reaction, 1 molecule of &apos;Phosphorylated platelet SEC1 protein&apos;, and 1 molecule of &apos;ADP&apos; are present. This reaction is mediated by the &apos;calcium-dependent protein kinase C activity&apos; of &apos;Activated Ca++ and DAG dependent PKC&apos;.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
          <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:vCard="http://www.w3.org/2001/vcard-rdf/3.0#" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:bqbiol="http://biomodels.net/biology-qualifiers/">
