      <reaction metaid="metaid_997" id="reaction_351341" name="Exocytosis of Proactivator polypeptide" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_161320">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">After Platelet activation &apos;Proactivator polypeptide&apos; from the lysosomal lumen is released in to the extracellular platelet releasate.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
