      <reaction metaid="metaid_1020" id="reaction_983285" name="RAD51B binds RAD51C" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_7660">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The Rad51-like proteins Rad51B and Rad51C form a highly stable complex. This complex assists Rad51 in the early stages of homologous recombination.</p>
        </notes>
