      <reaction metaid="metaid_1023" id="reaction_158766" name="fibrin multimer, crosslinked -&gt; fibrin digestion products (plasmin)" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_984">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Plasmin, generated at the surfaces of the fibrin clot by tissue plasminogen activator or at the surfaces of cells by urokinase plasminogen activator, catalyzes the hydrolysis of fibrin to soluble fragments (Chapman 1997).</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
