      <reaction metaid="metaid_1034" id="reaction_443831" name="14-3-3-zeta binds Raf1" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">14-3-3 family proteins can bind Raf1 and have been suggested to activate Raf1, but this has been refuted.</p>
