      <reaction metaid="metaid_1037" id="reaction_114689" name="PLC gamma 2-mediated PIP2 hydrolysis" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">At the beginning of this reaction, 1 molecule of &apos;1-Phosphatidyl-D-myo-inositol 4,5-bisphosphate&apos; is present. At the end of this reaction, 1 molecule of &apos;1D-myo-Inositol 1,4,5-trisphosphate&apos;, and 1 molecule of &apos;1,2-Diacylglycerol&apos; are present. This reaction is mediated by the &apos;phospholipase C activity&apos; of &apos;Phosphorylated phospholipase C gamma 2&apos;.</p>
        </notes>
