      <reaction metaid="metaid_1038" id="reaction_354124" name="Phosphorylation of pPTK2 by SRC" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The recruitment of FADK1 to active SRC leads to the efficient tyrosine phosphorylation of multiple additional sites on FADK1. SRC trans-phosphorylates FADK1 within the kinase doman activation loop (Y576 and Y577) and within the FADK1 C-terminal domain (Y861 and Y925).</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
