      <reaction metaid="metaid_1043" id="reaction_354060" name="Translocation of RIAM to plasma membrane" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Upon the production of activated Rap1A at the plasma membrane, RIAM interacts with Rap1A-GTP with its N-ter RA domain, and with its C-ter PH domain it interacts with PIP2.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
          <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:vCard="http://www.w3.org/2001/vcard-rdf/3.0#" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:bqbiol="http://biomodels.net/biology-qualifiers/">
