      <reaction metaid="metaid_1045" id="reaction_202709" name="JAM2 dimerises" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_876">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Apart from its well-established interaction with Integrin alpha4beta1 (VLA-4), JAM2 (JAM-B) is also known to homodimerize.</p>
        </notes>
