      <reaction metaid="metaid_1046" id="reaction_442273" name="VAV1 is a GEF for Rho/Rac family GTPases" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Vav family members are guanine nucleotide exchange factors (GEFs) for Rho-family GTPases. Vav1 is a GEF for Rac1, Rac2 and RhoG, and possibly RhoA and Cdc42</p>
        </notes>
