      <reaction metaid="metaid_1056" id="reaction_372697" name="Crk binding to p130cas" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Crk is an adaptor protein with one SH2 and two SH3 domains. It is involved in integrin mediated signalling and is recruited to the focal adhesion complexes by interacting with p130Cas or paxillin through its SH2 domain.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
