      <reaction metaid="metaid_1068" id="reaction_204873" name="Interaction of Tie2 and Shp2" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_876">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Shp2 interact with Tyr816 in the juxtamembrane region and Tyr1108 and Tyr1113, respectively, in the C-terminal tail region of Tie2/Tek.</p>
        </notes>
