      <reaction metaid="metaid_1071" id="reaction_442314" name="VAV3 is a GEF for Rho/Rac family kinases" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Vav3 is a guanine nucleotide exchange factors (GEF) for RhoA, RhoB and to a lesser extent Rac1.</p>
        </notes>
