      <reaction metaid="metaid_1079" id="reaction_140791" name="activated thrombin (factor IIa) + antithrombin III:heparan sulfate -&gt; thrombin:antithrombin III:heparan sulfate" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_984">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Activated thrombin binds to the antithrombin III:heparin complex on the cell surface.</p>
