      <reaction metaid="metaid_1081" id="reaction_432129" name="FGR binds and phosphorylates LRP8" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_70101">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Tyrosine phosphorylation of LDL:LRP8 is mediated by the Src-family kinase FGR, based on a correlation of increased LRP8 phosphorylation on LDL stimulation of platelets, and a transient increased co-precipitation of FGR with LRP8 upon LDL stimulation.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
