      <reaction metaid="metaid_1083" id="reaction_429529" name="Thrombin binding to GP1b:IX:V" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_984">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Thrombin binds to the GP1b-IX-V receptor during platelet aggregation. This leads to increased PAR activation, possibly due to favourable orientation of thrombin towards the PAR extracellular domain.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
          <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:vCard="http://www.w3.org/2001/vcard-rdf/3.0#" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:bqbiol="http://biomodels.net/biology-qualifiers/">
