      <reaction metaid="metaid_1106" id="reaction_158756" name="crosslinked fibrin multimer:tissue plasminogen activator (two-chain) + plasminogen -&gt; crosslinked fibrin multimer:tissue plasminogen activator (two-chain):plasminogen" reversible="false" fast="false" compartment="compartment_984">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">At the beginning of this reaction, 1 molecule of &apos;plasminogen&apos;, and 1 molecule of &apos;fibrin multimer, crosslinked:tissue plasminogen activator (two-chain)&apos; are present. At the end of this reaction, 1 molecule of &apos;fibrin multimer, crosslinked:tissue plasminogen activator (two-chain):plasminogen&apos; is present. This reaction takes place in the &apos;extracellular region&apos;.</p>
        </notes>
